data.description: Affordable turn-key property with options regarding highest and best use.  Currently configured as a single family home, the future owner may enjoy living here with its current floorplan, or modify the structure, so it conforms to the City's current assessed status as 2-unit property.  Many recent improvements include the construction of a second-floor laundry room; new flooring; and interior painting.  Why rent?  This is the property to see before it's gone.
